{"tid":2228301,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭若驊：金融x法律x科技 大灣區「一帶一路」龐大機遇","createTime":"2020-10-03T12:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T13:46:40.000Z","uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6cba957685bbdca02b16311be9acad1d036cf6e8","tid":2228301,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T12:32:38.000Z","msg":"律政司司長鄭若驊表示，現時國家的「一帶一路」建設和粵港澳大灣區規劃，為香港帶來龐大的機遇，香港應當發揮「一國兩制」下的獨特優勢，善用在金融、法律、科技等領域的經驗，配合大灣區的發展，以及在「一帶一路」沿線開拓業務，為香港的經濟注入新的動力之餘，更加可以為國家作出新的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊今天（1日）發表網誌。她在網誌指出，香港過去一直利用自身的優勢融合國家發展，體現了「同發展」、「共繁榮」，帶來的成就有目共睹。<br />\n<br />\n她又稱，《基本法》以法律把「一國兩制」成功落實，保持香港的繁榮和穩定。她稱，律政司正積極籌備《基本法》頒布30周年的法律高峰論壇，邀請專家從不同角度講解《憲法》、《基本法》以及「一國兩制」的關係，希望藉此提升社會對《憲法》和《基本法》的認知。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2767649\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2767649&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdl8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=7d85460e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2767649</a>"},{"pid":"ef97cef068fec82fa0778a6ad35d2ba0fda8be4d","tid":2228301,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T12:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f4af54182c68e920e39bcf895183b1fd5795d3","tid":2228301,"uid":36791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T12:38:42.000Z","msg":"大到馬雲咁，咪又係共產黨嘅"},{"pid":"9dfb2b564b8b0842ff5716fd3c725a7cd56e9617","tid":2228301,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T12:39:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09e1c2aba739a525ee91dc585b7fe334d6953b43","tid":2228301,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T12:39:22.000Z","msg":"出面攪唔到又咪死返去內循環<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5582